data.text: @xMasterWhox Let me know if people attack you. You don't deserve that
@xMasterWhox Pffff sounds hard indeed. Stay strong!!

@Gau88 It's intense times to be a Taylor fan tbh, there's so much hate. Liked & retweeted on my timeline, underneath every article, in completely off topic posts, underneath fanaccounts posts, there's just no safe spot, so I'm really fed up by it and explode easily
@xMasterWhox Hey I'd probably do the same if someone would trash my faves
@Gau88 It's alright, don't worry. I knew you're  nice person, so I just went totally Taylor defend mode lol
@xMasterWhox Yes sorry my head is a bit scrambled. So things may come out a bit harsher than I meant. Terribly sorry about that
@xMasterWhox It's never ok to bully. Disliking an artist isn't the same as bullying.

@xMasterWhox -- dates men to write songs about them later. I honestly try not to read any media opinions about her. But to me she's just someone I don't care about. I'm glad she's helped you and many others though.

@xMasterWhox I personally don't like her. Trash may be the wrong word here.  Kanye ofcourse is most definitely worse. Don't get me wrong. I don't hate her and I don't think she deserves all the horrible attacks. 

It's not fair how the media portrays her as some crazy woman who only --
@Gau88 y'all don't even know that woman and get hung up on incredible hateful bullshit, but it's okay to bully someone because she writes love songs I suppose. Yeah sure

@Gau88 about their problems with them in DMs, she got a pregnant fan an appointment with her Doctor and paid for it bc she had several miscarriages, and then she gets shitted on because she dares to write love songs. Because Media makes the best clicks for covering nothing but hate :-)

@Gau88 She's not trash in the slightest. She cares about her fans deeply, her music helped me feel empowered in the time I got bullied, she does a lot of charity, she invites forster kids and fans backstage/to private shows/secret sessions etc., she visits fans in hospitals & talks ~
@xMasterWhox Really can't stand both of them imho. Kanye is trash in a different way. But him being ubertrash doesn't mean she's not trash.
